{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/MathML","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Mathematical Markup Language (MathML)</strong> 是一種基於 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XML\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">XML (en-US)</a> 的延伸，可以用來描述數學符號以及保留數學式結構和內容。在這裡你可以找到參考文件, 範例以及工具。你可以從 <a href=\"http://fred-wang.github.io/MozSummitMathML/index.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">slides for the innovation fairs at Mozilla Summit 2013</a> 做個快速的大致瀏覽。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"mathml_references","title":"MathML references","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"mathml_element_reference\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML element reference (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>關於每一個 MathML element 的細節及其在桌面環境和瀏覽器的支援情形。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"mathml_attribute_reference\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML attribute reference (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>關於可改變 MathML element 外觀及行為的 MathML attributes。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"mathml_examples\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Examples\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML examples (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>MathML 的範例。透過這些範例你能更明白 MathML 是如何運作的。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"authoring_mathml\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/MathML/Authoring\">Authoring MathML</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>這裡提供一些關於 MathML 的建議以及小提示，包括適當的編輯器以及如何將他們和你的網頁內容整合。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"getting_help_from_the_community","title":"Getting help from the community","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"irc://irc.mozilla.org/%23mathml\">IRC channel</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://wiki.mozilla.org/MathML:Home_Page\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wiki used by Mozilla contributors</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/Math/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Math Home</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-math/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">www-math w3.org mail archive</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tools","title":"Tools","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"http://validator.w3.org\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Validator</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/de/firefox/addon/8969/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">FireMath Firefox add-on</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/collections/fred_wang/mathzilla/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Mathzilla Firefox add-on collection</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://dlmf.nist.gov/LaTeXML/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">LaTeXML</a> - 將 LaTeX 文件編譯為 HTML+MathML 網頁</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://webdemo.visionobjects.com/home.html#equation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Equation</a> - 將手寫的數學式轉換成 MathML 或 LaTeX</li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.mathjax.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathJax</a> - 使數學式的展現能跨瀏覽器的 JavaScript display engine</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_topics","title":"Related Topics","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG\">SVG</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.math","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/MathML/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"MathML references","id":"mathml_references"},{"text":"Getting help from the community","id":"getting_help_from_the_community"},{"text":"Tools","id":"tools"},{"text":"Related Topics","id":"related_topics"